<div class="bg-slate-900 min-h-screen">
  <%# Hero Section %>
  <div class="relative isolate overflow-hidden">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-24 sm:py-32 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-6xl">
          SecretCat 是如何工作的？
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">
          了解我们如何保护您的密码安全，以及为什么您可以信任 SecretCat
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# 主要内容区域 %>
  <div class="relative">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <%# 端到端加密 %>
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-indigo-400">安全性</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">
          端到端加密保护
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">
          您的密码在存储之前就已经被加密，只有您知道解密密钥。即使是我们的系统管理员也无法查看您的密码。
        </p>
      </div>

      <%# 工作原理步骤 %>
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
        <div class="space-y-16">
          <%# 步骤 1：主密码 %>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="relative rounded-xl bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 shadow-xl ring-1 ring-white/10">
              <div class="absolute -top-3 left-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-500 p-2">
                <span class="text-xl font-bold text-white">1</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="pt-4 text-xl font-bold leading-7 text-white">主密码的作用</h3>
              <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
                当您创建账号时，您设置的主密码永远不会被直接存储。相反，我们使用它来：
              </p>
              <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-gray-300">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                  </svg>
                  生成一个独特的加密密钥
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                  </svg>
                  创建一个安全的验证哈希
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <%# 步骤 2：密码加密 %>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="relative rounded-xl bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 shadow-xl ring-1 ring-white/10">
              <div class="absolute -top-3 left-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-500 p-2">
                <span class="text-xl font-bold text-white">2</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="pt-4 text-xl font-bold leading-7 text-white">密码加密过程</h3>
              <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
                当您保存新密码时：
              </p>
              <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-gray-300">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                  </svg>
                  使用 AES-256 加密算法（军事级别的加密标准）
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                  </svg>
                  每个密码都使用独特的加密密钥
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                  </svg>
                  加密在您的浏览器中完成，未加密的数据从不离开您的设备
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <%# 步骤 3：安全存储 %>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="relative rounded-xl bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 shadow-xl ring-1 ring-white/10">
              <div class="absolute -top-3 left-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-500 p-2">
                <span class="text-xl font-bold text-white">3</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="pt-4 text-xl font-bold leading-7 text-white">安全存储</h3>
              <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
                加密后的数据在我们的服务器上是如何保护的：
              </p>
              <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-gray-300">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                  </svg>
                  使用安全的数据库系统存储
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                  </svg>
                  定期备份确保数据不会丢失
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                  </svg>
                  所有传输都使用 HTTPS 加密
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <%# 步骤 4：访问密码 %>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="relative rounded-xl bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 shadow-xl ring-1 ring-white/10">
              <div class="absolute -top-3 left-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-500 p-2">
                <span class="text-xl font-bold text-white">4</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="pt-4 text-xl font-bold leading-7 text-white">访问您的密码</h3>
              <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
                当您需要使用密码时：
              </p>
              <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-gray-300">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                  </svg>
                  使用您的主密码生成解密密钥
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                  </svg>
                  在您的设备上本地解密数据
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                  </svg>
                  一键复制或自动填充到需要的地方
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <%# 安全建议 %>
        <div class="mt-16">
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-indigo-500/10 p-8 shadow-xl ring-1 ring-indigo-500/20">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold leading-7 text-white">保持安全的建议</h3>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-gray-300">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/>
                </svg>
                使用强主密码，不要与其他账号共用
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/>
                </svg>
                定期更换密码，使用密码生成器创建强密码
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/>
                </svg>
                在不信任的设备上使用后记得登出
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/>
                </svg>
                保持设备系统和浏览器及时更新
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <%# 开始使用按钮 %>
        <div class="mt-16 flex justify-center">
          <%= link_to "开始使用 SecretCat", signup_path, class: "rounded-xl bg-indigo-500 px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-lg hover:bg-indigo-400 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-400 transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-[1.02]" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div> 